text: Halyna Mosiychuk (Мосійчук Галина Василівна; died 12 April 2021) was a Soviet and Ukrainian composer. She made over a hundred songs, and several music videos and CDs. She won many awards and prizes for her works.На Рівненщині померла відома діячка культури Mosiychuk died in Dubno on 12 April 2021. ==References== Category:2021 deaths Category:Ukrainian composers Category:Soviet musicians Category:Ukrainian writers Category:Year of birth missing
